{"about_the_game":"Tired of those incremental games where you have to buy the first highlighted upgrade without thinking? Do you enjoy the rewarding feeling after unlocking hard earned stuff?<br><br>THIS-IS-YOUR-GAME!<br><br>I've been working and updating this game in my free time, as a hobby, during the last two years. I want to thank the  community for their support and feedback. Hope you enjoy it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_line.png?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_merge.png?t=1634373423\" /><br>Fuse two Pins to get an improved and stronger version. Sometimes they will result in a completely new and different Pin!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/fuseGif.gif?t=1634373423\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/fuseGif2.gif?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_line.png?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_plan.png?t=1634373423\" /><br>Plan your strategy. Add Pins into a formation, each Formation with its own spcial bonus, slots amount and slot types. Choose the best combination for each situation.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_tipos.png?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_line.png?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_explore.png?t=1634373423\" /><br>Explore different locations. Each with their own enemies, materials, and drops. Advance through zones and maps to find new crafting blueprints and unlock new features!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_maps.png?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_line.png?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_tuning.png?t=1634373423\" /><br>Tune and improve your attack Pins stats like their power and HP or even the chance of multihit! Can you get S+ Rank tunes on all the 11 stats?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_line.png?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_tower.png?t=1634373423\" /><br>Follow the clues and unlock The Tower. Send expeditions to find new floors with randomized enemies and loot, keep the ones you like and build your own Tower!  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_towergif.gif?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_line.png?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_prestige.png?t=1634373423\" /><br>Of course there is a prestige mechanic! Start a new season and sacrifice some progress to unlock over 200 powerful upgrades. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/seasonAnim.gif?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_line.png?t=1634373423\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 250 different Pins to collect<br></li><li>25 different formations with their own bonuses to fit your Pins. Plan your strategy!<br></li><li>130+ enemies in 12 different zones<br></li><li>60+ crafting blueprints to unlock new Pins, features and QoL<br></li><li>70+ Trophies to boost game mechanics<br></li><li>170+ ingame achievements<br></li><li>Prestige system and Black Market, together with 400+ upgrades and QoL stuff to unlock<br></li><li>Master the Art of Alchemy to find new Pins<br></li><li>Merge, tune, level up, dismantle, synthesize and much more.</li></ul><br>I already did too many spoilers :P<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709920/extras/c_line.png?t=1634373423\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"OVERCHARGE I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709920/df652087375c92433b594cf32439db3420743004.jpg"},{"name":"OVERCHARGE II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709920/5a67cfa166faac867933461d62b45b8afaae5bc1.jpg"},{"name":"OVERCHARGE III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709920/a87d1f69a46027e222a6aff55824045e2123dea8.jpg"},{"name":"OVERCHARGE IV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709920/538b1668c4b0c46662d90035395bebaa21c0545c.jpg"},{"name":"OVERCHARGE V","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709920/d3fbb1f8890b200feda11399d934ac11259636bc.jpg"},{"name":"LEADICATOR I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709920/d9ab56d17590da2fb73d98bddf20b26b39d37c27.jpg"},{"name":"LEADICATOR II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709920/291ce62e05707b721896e452adb362a25b1e1494.jpg"